snippet.title: Shri Ram Lalla Pran Pratishtha LIVE | PM Modi attends Pran Pratishtha of Shri Ram in Ayodhya
snippet.description:
Prime Minister Narendra Modi attended and addressed the Pran Pratishtha event of Shri Ram in Ayodhya. The auspicious and mega Pran Pratishtha ceremony of Shri Ram Lalla's idol in the newly built Ram Janmabhoomi Temple took place in the temple town of Ayodhya on January 22. Several events and rituals were lined up for the Pran-Pratishtha ceremony including a musical event titled ‘Mangal Dhwani’.

snippet.title: Meera Road पर जिन दुकानदारों की दुकान पर चला बुलडोज़र, उन्होंने क्या बताया? (BBC Hindi)
snippet.description:
22 जनवरी को अयोध्या के श्रीराम मंदिर में प्राण प्रतिष्ठा कार्यक्रम से एक दिन पहले रविवार की शाम मीरा रोड के नया नगर इलाक़े से होकर एक जुलूस गुज़र रहा था. इस जुलूस पर कथित तौर पर पथराव की घटना के बाद दो गुटों में भिड़ंत हो गई थी, जिसके बाद यहां बड़ी संख्या में सुरक्षाबलों की तैनाती कर दी गई थी. इसके बाद, मंगलवार को नगर निगम ने इस इलाक़े में कुछ दुकानों पर बुलडोज़र चलाया था. नगर निगम का कहना था कि यह कार्रवाई अवैध निर्माण हटाने के लिए की गई है. लेकिन जिन दुकानदारों की दुकान टूटी, उन्होंने क्या बताया...

रिपोर्ट: दीपाली जगताप
शूट: शाहिद शेख़
एडिटिंग: नीलेश भोसले

#mumbai #meeraroad #buldozer 

* ऐसे ही और दिलचस्प वीडियो देखने के लिए चैनल सब्सक्राइब ज़रूर करें-
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCN7B-QD0Qgn2boVH5Q0pOWg?disable_polymer=true

* बीबीसी हिंदी से आप इन सोशल मीडिया चैनल्स पर भी जुड़ सकते हैं-

snippet.title: Ayodhya Ram Mandir: राम मंदिर पहुंचे PM Modi, देखिए Pran Pratishtha से पहले क्या किया | Aaj Tak
snippet.description:

snippet.title: Ayodhya Ram Mandir: Ramlala के दर्शन कर Jackie Shroff, Ayushmann Khurrana जैसे दिग्गज क्या बोले?
snippet.description:

snippet.title: Chintu's Take : Samarth Jurel Spills Bigg Boss 17 Beans - Isha Malviya and More Unveiled!
snippet.description:
Get ready for a podcast party with Samarth Jurel also knwon as Chintu , straight out of Bigg Boss! He spills the scoop on his journey in Bigg Boss House  – the crazy highs, hilarious lows, and all the inside gossip. Listen in as he spills the tea on his friendships and clashes with other contestants. It's like a backstage pass to Bigg Boss life, packed with laughs, drama, and Samarth's awesome stories! 

#bhartisingh #harshlimbachiya #samarthjurel  #podcast

(46:39) - End

snippet.description:
Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu Naatu Guntalu Dhiddina Kapuram MCM

Cricket Stars :- https://abr.ge/ms8isg 
Send Screen Shots To :- community@golive.games

Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu releases a new Epsiode in which a funny scene starts with Rosy Madam and Vegetables seller which turns to a discussion between komalis father. Komali calls Madhu and asks him to meet at Pedha Cheruvu along with Mahesh. Both Madhu and Mahesh meets Komali in the evening where Komali asks for a suggestion. Mahesh suggests a plan and Naatu Guntalu Gang gets ready for the action. Watch this Guntala Diddhina Kaapuram to have an amazing time. We are very near to 5 Million Subscribers 🙏🏻

snippet.title: मंदिर के उद्घाटन पर क्या बोला अंबानी परिवार?
snippet.description:
#mukeshambani #nitaambani #reliance #ayodhya #ayodhyarammandir #pranpratishtha 
राम मंदिर में प्राण प्रतिष्ठा समारोह में शामिल होने के लिए पूरे देश से लोग अयोध्या पहुंच रहे हैं। इस समारोह में देश के सबसे अमीर मुकेश अंबानी भी अपने पूरे परिवार के साथ इस कार्यक्रम का हिस्सा बनने के लिए पहुंचे हैं। इस दौरान उन्होंने कहा कि इस पल का सक्षी बनना सौभाग्या की बात है। देखें नीता अंबानी ने क्या कहा?

बिजनेस जगत की हर बड़ी खबर, उनसे जुड़े एक्सप्लेनर वीडियो, बिजनेस शख्सियत  की दिलचस्प कहानियां, रियल एस्टेट, गोल्ड, ऑटो सेक्टर, स्टार्टअप्स,  शेयर बाजार, सेंसेक्स और पर्सलन फाइनेंस जैसे विषयों की जानकारी हासिल करने के लिए जुड़े बिजनेस टुडे हिंदी से। यहां आपकों म्यूचुअल फंड, एसआईपी, इक्विटी, बीमा, लोन्स, पेंशन, रिटायरमेंट योजनाओं के बारे में आसान भाषा में मिलेगी दिलचस्प जानकारी। 

आप हमें यहां फॉलो कर सकते हैं: 

वेबसाइट: https://www.bazaar.businesstoday.in 

फेसबुक: https://www.facebook.com/businesstodaybazaar

ट्विटर:  https://twitter.com/BT_Bazaar

इंस्टाग्राम: https://www.instagram.com/bt_bazaar/

snippet.title: Isha : ‘Abhishek didn't have mental health issues,he was holidaying in Goa then..!’ | Bigg Boss 17
snippet.description:
In an exclusive chat with Bigg Boss 17 evicted contestant Isha Malviya, she speaks about how Abhishe Kumar used Khanzaadi as a distraction. She also says why Abhishek crying during her eviction was fake.

She speaks about whether she regrets getting intimate with Samarth Jurel in the house and why she doesn't regret calling Mannara a bar dancer.

She also reveals whether Ankita Lokhande has fallen in love with Munawar Faruqui and why there should be a ghatiyapan's statue made for Munawar.

snippet.title: Bus Depot पर Bhelpuri बेचते हुए Spot किए गए Daya |CID |Latest Episode |Unlimited Action |20 Jan 2024
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Crime: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzXpAx4v6rFLYXkJZ5nmSvQ?sub_confirmation=1

In this intriguing case, the CID team delves into the abduction of the wife of a prominent and wealthy businessman. The kidnappers demand a peculiar ransom of 5 crores, to be delivered in 5 instalments at 5 different locations. As CID attempts to unravel this complex and strategic plot, they find themselves consistently outsmarted by the cunning perpetrators. Suspecting the involvement of an insider, CID faces the challenge of identifying the traitor within the businessman's circle. Watch this gripping episode to uncover the twists and turns in the pursuit of the kidnapper.

Show Name: CID 
Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
• Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
• Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
• Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
• Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
• Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
• Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode: 948
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh

#CID #सीआईडी #cid2024  #CrimeThrillers #CrimeMysteries #Mysteries #Horror #LIVCrime #NewCID #Crime #NewCID #LatestCID

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

Click here to watch more episodes of CID Best From TV :
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL0y08jtgaKIUYuRlCxU2dJkUtocAxRIme

Episode 3988: Popatlal's Date With Anokhi
--------------------------------------------------------
Popatlal gets ready to meet Anokhi, and Sodhi adds a romantic touch to his car for a pleasant time. Champaklal informs Jethalal about his and Tapu Sena's plan to attend a bhajan. Eventually, Popatlal takes Anokhi on a drive.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: कल के आनंद के लिए सौ-सौ न्योछावर मेरे सरकार ❤️🙏 |अयोध्या | राम मंदिर प्राण प्रतिष्ठा
snippet.description:
इष्टदेव मम बालक रामा। 
सोभा बपुष कोटि सत कामा॥
निज प्रभु बदन निहारि निहारी। 
लोचन सुफल करउँ उरगारी ॥😢❤️🙏
 कल के परमानंद के लिए सौ-सौ दंडवत् मेरे सरकार 🙏
#kumarvishwas #ayodhya #rammandir 
Follow us on :- 

YouTube :- http://youtube.com/KumarVishwas
Facebook :- https://www.facebook.com/KumarVishwas
Twitter :- https://twitter.com/DrKumarVishwas
Instagram :- https://www.instagram.com/KumarVishwas

Subscribe To Our Other YouTube Channels:-

Apne Apne Ram    : https://www.youtube.com/@ApneApneRamOfficial
  
The KV Studio        : https://www.youtube.com/@TheKVStudio

Apne Apne Shyam : https://www.youtube.com/@ApneApneShyamOfficial

-------------------------------------------------------------------
About Dr Kumar Vishwas :

The people who make history are the ones who not only give their life to their career but also give their career a new life. When the career is that of a poet, every step is a risk. Kumar Vishwas is one such poet who has gifted himself an era of such a popularity which other poets cant’t even dream of.
Kumar Vishwas is a poet who went beyond the stereotypical norms of ‘Kavi Sammelan’ or poetic functions and made it a performer’s stage. He has mastered and excelled in all aspects in whatever he has done. Dr Kumar Vishwas has been doing this since years just with a mic and his poems and wits in his soulful voice.
His popularity can be guessed by the fact that the audience sings his verses with him, he has crafted a new dimension by rejuvenating the structure and mechanics of Hindi poetry and Kavi Sammelan.
 
Recently, Dr. Kumar Vishwas has started hosting energy sessions popularly Known as Apne Apne Ram and Apne Apne Shyam where he talks about life skills of Shri Ram’s and Shri Krishna's life, and the applicability of the same in one’s own life to over come the challenges and social concerns we come across in our life.

snippet.title: Sunday Brunch With Nitin Gadkari & Kamiya Jani Over Vadapav & Chinese Food | EP 123 | Curly Tales
snippet.description:
He is a foodie first, and a politician second. Minister of Road, Transport and Highways, Nitin Gadkari invites Kamiya Jani to his Delhi residence for a delectable Maharashtrian meal. From Sabudana Vada, Vada Pav, and Bread Pakoda to Chinese dishes, Mr Gadkari also shares recipes of his favorite food dishes. We bet you will be entertained throughout! P

Hailing from Nagpur, his impactful work has won the hearts of the entire nation. Beyond politics, his passion for food is not a hidden affair. Watch this episode as we delve deep into his food choices, recipes & also the future of Road travel 🌟🍽️

Included with Prime Video: Thousands of acclaimed TV shows & movies across languages & geographies, including Indian films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Shakuntala Devi, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, and HOME, along with Indian-produced Amazon Original series like Farzi, Jubilee, Dahaad, The Family Man, Mirzapur, Made in Heaven, Four More Shots Please!, Mumbai Diaries 26/11, Suzhal – The Vortex, Modern Love, Paatal Lok, Bandish Bandits, Guilty Minds, Cinema Marte Dum Tak, and Amazon Original movies like Maja Ma & Ammu. Also included are popular global Amazon Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Reacher, Tom Clancy's Jack Ryan, The Boys, Hunters, Fleabag, The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel, & many more, available for unlimited streaming as part of a Prime membership. Prime Video includes content across Hindi, Marathi, Gujarati, Tamil, Telugu, Kannada, Malayalam, Punjabi, & Bengali. 
Prime Video Mobile Edition: Consumers can also enjoy Prime Video’s exclusive content library with Prime Video Mobile Edition at ₹599 per year. This single-user, mobile-only annual video plan offers everyone access to high-quality entertainment exclusively on their mobile devices. Users can sign-up for this plan via the Prime Video app (on Android) or website. 
Instant Access: Prime Members can watch anywhere, anytime on the Prime Video app for smart TVs, mobile devices, Fire TV, Fire TV stick, Fire tablets, Apple TV, & multiple gaming devices. Prime Video is also available to consumers through Airtel and Vodafone pre-paid & post-paid subscription plans. In the Prime Video app, Prime members can download episodes on their mobile devices & tablets & watch anywhere offline at no additional cost.
Enhanced experiences: Make the most of every viewing with 4K Ultra HD- & High Dynamic Range (HDR)-compatible content. Go behind the scenes of your favourite movies & TV shows with exclusive X-Ray access, powered by IMDb. Save it for later with select mobile downloads for offline viewing. 
Video Entertainment Marketplace: In addition to a Prime Video subscription, customers can also purchase add-on subscriptions to other streaming services, as well as, get rental access to movies on Prime Video. Prime Video Channels: Prime Video Channels offers friction-free & convenient access to a wide range of premium content from multiple video streaming services all available at a single destination – Prime Video website & apps. Prime Members can buy add-on subscriptions & enjoy a hassle-free entertainment experience, simplified discovery, frictionless payments, & more. Rent: Consumers can enjoy even more movies from new releases to classic favourites, available to rent – no Prime membership required. View titles available by visiting primevideo.com/store. The rental destination can be accessed via the STORE tab on primevideo.com & the Prime Video app on Android smart phones, smart-TVs, connected STBs, & Fire TV stick.

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3987: Jethalal Has Jalebi And Fafda
--------------------------------------------------------
Popatlal visits the temple to pray for his relationship with Anokhi. Meanwhile, Jethalal craves jalebi and fafda, contemplating inviting Taarak and even Babita to join. Subsequently, Jethalal invites Taarak to breakfast, and Taarak waits for Anjali to leave so he can discreetly visit Jethalal's house.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3987, 22 Jan 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.
